N:awesome-agent-skills
D:Routing front door for the Awesome Agent Skills collection (Shubhamsaboo/awesome-llm-apps) — 19 expert-persona skills + a self-improving optimizer in 6 reference pipelines: coding (python-expert, code-reviewer, debugger, fullstack-developer), research (deep-research, fact-checker, academic-researcher), writing (technical-writer, content-creator, editor, email-drafter, meeting-notes), planning (project-planner, sprint-planner, strategy-advisor, decision-helper, ux-designer), data (data-analyst, visualization-expert), self-improving (ADK multi-agent skill optimizer). Plugin (upstream): `npx skills add shubhamsaboo/awesome-agent-skills`
G:awesome-agent-skills agent-skills code-review debugging python fullstack deep-research fact-check academic technical-writing content editing email meeting-notes project-planning sprint strategy decision ux data-analysis visualization skill-optimization

P[6]{pipeline,personas}:
  coding,python-expert · code-reviewer · debugger · fullstack-developer
  research,deep-research · fact-checker · academic-researcher
  writing,technical-writer · content-creator · editor · email-drafter · meeting-notes
  planning,project-planner · sprint-planner · strategy-advisor · decision-helper · ux-designer
  data,data-analyst · visualization-expert
  self-improving,ADK Executor+Analyst+Mutator skill optimizer (Google ADK + Gemini)

U[5]:
  Work maps to an expert persona (review code, debug, research, write docs, plan, decide, design, analyze data)
  Want a consistent framework + output format for a common knowledge-work task
  Verify a claim or fact-check a source (research pipeline)
  Break a project/sprint down, make a decision matrix, or design a user flow (planning pipeline)
  Optimize an existing agent skill until it passes its evals (self-improving pipeline)

S[4]{n,action,details}:
  1,Pick pipeline + persona,Classify against the routing table; state "pipeline → persona" explicitly before producing output
  2,Load the persona framework,Read references/<pipeline>-pipeline.md and adopt that persona's process, checklists, and output format
  3,Execute with discipline,Code: Security→Performance→Correctness→Maintainability · Research: evidence-first, never fabricate citations · Debug: root cause before fix
  4,Return the persona output packet,Use the persona's structured format; close with a one-line Next step pointing to a follow-on persona when relevant
